    public interface NotInCurrencySilo
extends com.guidewire.bc.domain.accounting.gen.NotInCurrencySiloStubI
    NotInCurrencySilo is implemented by entities that are explicitly not part of a currency silo. CurrencySilo-ed entities have restrictions on the relationships they have with each other, in that two CurrencySilo-ed entities can only be put in a relationship if they operate using the same currency. Note: Any entity that has a Currency field must implement exactly one of the delegates: InCurrencySilo or NotInCurrencySilo.
